confexec
========

author: itouhiro



Description
-----------

confirm existance of the directory and execute (for Windows)


This program will do:

- Wait seconds (-w 60)
- Check existance of the directory (-d "r:\cap")
- Execute ("C:\bin\foo.exe -a 1 -f \"r:\cap\aa.jpg\"")



Usage
-----

see http://d.hatena.ne.jp/itouhiro/20120118



